Description:
Quality People ATL (QPAtl) represents a gathering of current and aspiring Quality and Process Improvement practitioners, from all industries and diverse backgrounds

Quality People ATL mission is built on QUALITY PEOPLE SUPPORTING QUALITY PEOPLE

QPAtl was formed with the following goals and objectives:
• Create an effective forum for meeting and networking;
• Share and leverage knowledge, lessons learned, other notable best practices;
• Develop a specialized cohort of thought leaders;
• Educate and develop our skills;
• Support career development, transitions, and other job connecting opportunities.
